    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missi 是一款风格舒适的点击冒险游戏，采用水彩画风格。利用过去冒险中的线索来解开谜题。尝试收集药草为生病的小老鼠治疗，同时智胜蘑菇蜘蛛和乌鸦王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/1d71d3dd0f69df4320edf38cafe55219.poster.avif?t=1764594363\" width=616 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/1d71d3dd0f69df4320edf38cafe55219.webm?t=1764594363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/1d71d3dd0f69df4320edf38cafe55219.mp4?t=1764594363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>魔幻之旅与角色</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >勇敢的小老鼠 Missi 开始了一段令人兴奋的旅程，在这里她会遇到神奇的生物并解开许多独特的谜题。让一座龙雕像复活，与沼泽女巫一起煮药，并参与其他童话般的冒险。这款氛围浓厚的 2D 点击冒险游戏的多彩世界中的友好居民，随时准备帮助你寻找物品或解决谜题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/f77e63e01de1f01d0cf88ab4710a70ad.avif?t=1764594363\" width=616 height=240 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>众多谜题</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Missi 中，有许多不同类型的谜题等待着你，其中一些可能相当具有挑战性。别忘了查看素描本，那里收集了你之前冒险的片段，仔细探索这个神奇世界的每个角落寻找线索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/127698e7152a85003d835f5d422e6fe8.poster.avif?t=1764594363\" width=616 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/127698e7152a85003d835f5d422e6fe8.webm?t=1764594363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >手绘动画</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missi 的角色和世界通过完全手绘的逐帧动画栩栩如生。我们制作了两千多帧，捕捉活生生的插画的温暖，带领玩家沉浸在神奇旅程的氛围中。这让游戏感觉就像儿童书籍的页面在你的屏幕上展开。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/56cbf94f990f8e3a723bd4fb7379a205.poster.avif?t=1764594363\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/56cbf94f990f8e3a723bd4fb7379a205.webm?t=1764594363\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/56cbf94f990f8e3a723bd4fb7379a205.mp4?t=1764594363\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>水彩画美学</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中的插图采用可爱的水彩风格绘制。不需要竞争或战斗。只需享受这款舒适的游戏，揭开老鼠洞的秘密，帮助天文学家青蛙，或在鱼岛上拯救干渴的曼德拉草。游戏中几乎没有文字，所有对话都是以可爱的图画形式呈现的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3161960/extras/d324595f8a3c8726477a486615bc417b.avif?t=1764594363\" width=616 height=240 /></span></h2>",
